The paper focuses on facial micro-expression recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of Long Short-term Memory (LSTM) module also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also involves visualizations of the CNN's predictions, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the application of facial micro-expression recognition has implications in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
